@Grimsdottir: That is weird. There isn't any fundamental difference (if I didn't make some mistakes...) between the version on userstyles.org and the newest one. I'm quite sure it's because of the code in the bottom for specific sites.
Like for latest comments on ZeroBlog
```
/* ZeroTalk */
@-moz-document regexp("^https?://.*/Talk.ZeroNetwork.bit/.*"),
regexp("^https?://.*/0list.bit/.*")
{
.comment {
background-color: #242424 !important;
}
}
```
Sorry I can't think of any possible cause. If you have time and interest, you can experiment it and find out the culprit by yourself :3
